{"type":"message","id":"3fda3484","parentId":"ae619368","timestamp":"2026-04-16T15:23:18.985Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0143781879c152dd0169e0fee4a52081919311c1fe67ea3c8c\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp4P7mxSC4iXdkf_iF1IC3J-hGFWLnWKuamr4rYaUmWrFU9zFGOz93wOc9hPT8OuwxqTAVgMV3c0ZDP7UlF7BYT-5l4FAmucaGU9x35i6hzjpMrwkEyFYVvrmUchA9wNRDzKr0kT58yJVNHgGQqW58NBygv663bE6tUYVLKVM-wnWVdmiliaGItJyAXJOuTQ4krMIXyiyUaE78YuFOBkn5l3e4HRsuC7bZfsui7oDg-f_1wjY5ADRWj_WkALf0TGPUwVQ2cuQc_J5K7e5zO1U74DDzSB8c6zpSFfeTNo0I-b0GgnRXlO5eeeTRiRVI7oyafINX7LRh16-egUZlEntVA_B8cLoYNKmVGjq_jizOMki02Kz_wxUMobFkc2T4FJXLaOwO8w7sh1ZGQsxp-4gik0ykFrAzL6PzN1OzHS6dQ-6DIU28D5q5aFHFTbF5eyZ2nbgdl5wor2M2Lh_s967oWwqr9ATRBgRQ_k6dC1Sxu4JiPTfsQj9LvposrTgXMUitwDeGY04QJri5rDBnLnLy0tBd0ClmWqRmdoauNnOBb8OCIPAGqjk4SkCa-E_zuJbhdrnTuHoHZfLn12bDej6iTSV1qdgg6uuBRDGUjUEl6097NW5YmBO4RqaTH9HduXPjIm1-ULnvdEoNTK1RVQJFuLP-WsaZff2p-fPW-cUne7XKdmvq7q5EcxsmwYNFZ36eN16CQaY8SYNivG-AKoKT3JT-8iHGXsNhks2xDwrL9smupYMx8ZyE748nKUQ8o0OrnQAg7h9Q5pxNz3WvWLNU0KAqNCLM4RBSj9LJHLpV8ydlJUmlDLCNT_IIkM-u91-A6gVTLJfLKcTcVQr4-lC5FoV4olm9_lVR084A3_JUD5NzezZg4wo7v-PmIuJsyY7LkHorzcF1ft4a-NHdT-woZE6KCYh_x8bQ7v7mrkE6Gs0wcmA=\",\"summary\":[]}"},{"type":"text","text":"I’m going to quickly inspect the existing Apollo discussion material in `cleam/` and then I’ll turn that into a structured tasking map.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0143781879c152dd0169e0fee62ae08191b8069ac772ac62a8\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_kIDIX2TG7qzYPBJm6ILgzeO5|fc_0143781879c152dd0169e0fee64bec81919bc15fa3beae1ecf","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /home/node/.openclaw/workspace/cleam -maxdepth 3 \\( -type f -o -type l \\) | sort | sed 's#^#/##'","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":20},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"find /home/node/.openclaw/workspace/cleam -maxdepth 3 \\\\( -type f -o -type l \\\\) | sort | sed 's#^#/##'\",\"yieldMs\":10000,\"t