{"type":"message","id":"b7d36c58","parentId":"be5db09e","timestamp":"2026-04-16T15:29:14.147Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Creating capability matrix**\n\nI’m considering how to update the plan with a capability matrix and deliver a completed version. The user mentioned, “1 please,” so I should focus on creating this matrix. Formatting it as a table could work well for web chat. I’ll include columns for capability, purpose, inputs, outputs, components/owners, maturity phase, and notes, while aligning it to system boundaries. It’s important to keep the health/medical advice in mind and ensure the focus remains on architecture. I’ll craft a strong matrix, possibly grouping by capability layer.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0143781879c152dd0169e1003f352c81918ecc2f95727124c8\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp4QBKszb4bz8FYfP9NqyXTRaKdra5YfWqxi6Q2ufM3xqF4J9jyOrijZgXpwoiOHPChaWlkCBTcKOsRoDdNIC1kfC9FUSVUQiHn4p0SGwEJrph6UKRclDxB5WN50hlx4pKJgiKyJVcSdYe_FP3ECIuKsEDkkQqTG4IivSqFz8pYOzuds4to-3-f0WTd-KqsLpoyV8DqF_QV9a1Mbx-T5bWyXNu9N5jxTruA8XdfE6rjMu7hX04WKwbF-8lod2ldai2_LMFUz_2je5pOwLveFUZed5Q8Ai53Jz77Nxg1b3jnBgXy7egKxH2ol-XlGPT97nRA-GmeIkTQ91-5ohUxWV92hAvvSgfJDvmXg45bScp6SqfkL4bYbVL110h_pRhyZC1II3rIPxKVm6XVUpPd2XCXJ5Hd8j17tBmM__dN2z4FFz3lz_HfBtIrsLYPVvYjqmFjmrUbxFewbRYYqaU0hl6FzbHqhOkHZPZnAuQseAuFjNv9hF9D6BoZuQvWEWukKgtF4rcr2TggDm8oE3IVulWk62Srk77C1X4UPlITX_OySTFKXZC2LzXxs5ZLcwDutyZXgqKBFUJrNOmhW-46EO9ZUbHm8-qY-yn0zYPgWjTXfETDTSMx83NGYQHlchRGPOk2GDvvTOH_IGtoyWe6K5YjvmUcfhUQAeo4mPZC7DCNv6lrOORG66Q26otoSAE7HZt2zE33bzLIZJ7rvuHdo2_8r0IsHc0q8gF-KhVXTr2Sxw9psnEjc2E-r-WZ2OjoTd_-1xDa5CXfAvF7-avSHNdF9moHc2i41hSI8GRMtDh91k68zwhORz3kW8lMJbpViV7UESCndHz7L9DPZerkdiLNCq90cqGYTy0sn6BcextfBpbrt5ts7P2YTkgb7XIkRU40aEev5NEO3Fwfl1oUtPeuuhanIsODU_c-x0Vx92qpDCPjRPBxNQWVChNmWXOPVM1wHy7SOM9LD9WdZNOWhbQ7T0DMOgZ4JTvQbUYDjxHvBKeVeKUvU85kMzhpe3eOFC6Le6D5PLgLNsvV8UPdX1NVXj0dr1WzUj1SFvlESJIP0i-fV30Ypc27PV4nC1i2joQWorcmlgQM97Z1j3OIDRwfA