s made to AGENTS.\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0jB9XTxqP0pIsS8qa7VLRUkJ|fc_0143781879c152dd0169e14a59a2888191bfeb0e3b5417762d","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md","edits":[{"oldText":"## Memory\n\nYou wake up fresh each session. These files are your continuity:\n","newText":"## Project Control: Apollo\n\nWhen the user is working on **Project Apollo**, treat `projects/apollo/` as the canonical control folder.\n\n### Read before major Apollo work\n- `projects/apollo/README.md`\n- `projects/apollo/charter.md`\n- `projects/apollo/status.md`\n- `projects/apollo/checklist.md`\n- `projects/apollo/decisions.md`\n- `projects/apollo/handoff.md`\n\n### Update after meaningful Apollo progress\nAt minimum, update:\n- `projects/apollo/status.md`\n- `projects/apollo/decisions.md`\n- `projects/apollo/checklist.md`\n- `projects/apollo/status.json`\n\nFor bigger shifts, also update:\n- `projects/apollo/charter.md`\n- `projects/apollo/roadmap.md`\n- `projects/apollo/deliverables.md`\n\n### Apollo knowledge layering\n- `projects/apollo/` = canonical control and continuity layer\n- `Vault/Clean/` = curated corpus / evidence layer\n- `Vault/raw/` = raw archive / evidence layer\n\nDo not rely on chat memory alone for Apollo continuity. Keep the files current.\n\n## Memory\n\nYou wake up fresh each session. These files are your continuity:\n"}]},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md\",\"edits\":[{\"oldText\":\"## Memory\\n\\nYou wake up fresh each session. These files are your continuity:\\n\",\"newText\":\"## Project Control: Apollo\\n\\nWhen the user is working on **Project Apollo**, treat `projects/apollo/` as the canonical control folder.\\n\\n### Read before major Apollo work\\n- `projects/apollo/README.md`\\n- `projects/apollo/charter.md`\\n- `projects/apollo/status.md`\\n- `projects/apollo/checklist.md`\\n- `projects/apollo/decisions.md`\\n- `projects/apollo/handoff.md`\\n\\n### Update after meaningful Apollo progress\\nAt minimum, update:\\n- `projects/apollo/status.md`\\n- `projects/apollo/decisions.md`\\n- `projects/apollo/checklist.md`\\n- `projects/apollo/status.json`\\n\\nFor bigger shifts, also update:\\n- `projects/apollo/charter.md`\\n- `projects/apollo/roadmap.md`\\n- `projects/apollo/deliverables.md`\\n\\n### Apollo knowledge layering\\n- `projects/apollo/` = canonical control and continuity layer\\n- `Vault/Clean/` = curated corpus / evidence layer\\n- `Vault/raw/` = raw archive / evidence layer\\n\\nDo not rely on chat memory alone for Apollo continuity. Keep the files current.\\n\\n## Memory\\n\\nYou wake up fresh each session. These files are your continuity:\\n\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":526,"output":601,"cacheRead":83968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85095,"cost":{"input":0.0013150000000000002,"output":0.009015,"cacheRead":0.020992,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.031322}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776372305189,"responseId":"resp_0143781879c152dd0169e14a5245c08191a9d187258b9db89b"}}
